      "heading": "Detailed description",
      "text": "The MikroTik K-65 rackmount ears are a reliable and practical mounting solution designed specifically for the RB4011 series routers. Made from high-quality, durable metal, these rack ears allow you to securely install your RB4011 device into a standard 19-inch server rack, ensuring a clean, professional look for your network setup. The precise design guarantees a perfect fit and stable support, keeping your equipment safely in place even in demanding environments. Ideal for use in data centers, offices, or advanced home networks, the K-65 rackmount ears make it easy to integrate your MikroTik device into an organized and efficient rack system. Whether you are expanding your existing infrastructure or setting up a new installation, the K-65 provides a simple, space-saving, and long-lasting solution for mounting your RB4011 router securely and neatly."
